* Iron Raptor snarled under her breath, how could she be so stupid?!!!
She switched her com-link to the Coded frequency and spoke into it...*

" Sorry about that, Sir. My mistake. I'm locked in on your signature, are 
there any specific orders that you need me to follow? Any specific place you 
wish me to strike?"

* It wasn't long until Iron Raptor came to the clearing that the Pred base 
stood in and hid in the surrounding brush, she looked it over and judged 
where she should attack first.
If Liono didn't respond within a few clicks she would advance into the 
Predacon base and strike quietly, cutting the power and so on.*
